vote.title: Authorize a public hearing, to be held on November 9, 2022, to receive comments regarding adoption of a Community Development Program for the period January 1, 2023 through January 1, 2025, and a public hearing to be held December 14, 2022, to receive comments regarding adoption of the new Economic Development Incentive Policy for the period January 1, 2023 through January 1, 2025 - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
